data.description: This 4-bedroom, 3.5-bath home has so much to offer! The main floor boasts a versatile office or 4th bedroom, along with spacious living areas, while the second floor hosts three bedrooms and two full baths. Enjoy a plethora of recent updates, including sleek kitchen cabinets with stunning granite countertops, ceramic tile flooring, fresh interior paint, a new garage door, and a durable metal roof. Stay comfortable year-round with the new central heating and air conditioning units installed in 2020, with upgraded ductwork. The kitchen appliances have been updated in recent years, and the cozy electric fireplace adds charm and warmth. Step outside to your private oasis, featuring a fenced backyard with a fire pit and the shade of mature trees. Don't miss your chance to view this property 2023-10-26
